- console_printer: more info when measuring related hwd counters, e.g. instruction per cycle
- multiplexing on hwd counters
- more examples / doc
- passing function, with fixed arguments, e.g. s.add("f(5,6)", &f, 5, 6)
- passing function with generated arguments
- chrono::init is not supported on most platforms
- (multiple) printers via ctor
